---
title: Little good is better than abundance of evil
---

Say, "Not equal are the evil and the good, although the abundance of evil might impress you." So fear Allah, O you of understanding, that you may be successful. [Quran surah Mayedah (5): verse 100]

Explain this verse from Tafsir Ibn Kathir page 203

Talk about the greediness of modern capitalism and the importance of being content on what Allah gave to us. 